Introduction

Pongsapak Oudompoch, known as Santa, is a Thai actor, singer, and member of the project boy group PROJECT JASP.ER under RISER MUSIC. The group debuted on December 19, 2024, with the single "แรงอีกนิด (SADISTIC)."

Santa first gained recognition as a contestant in GMMTV's "Thailand School Star 2019" and began his acting career in 2021 with Studio Wabi Sabi, debuting in the series "7 Project." He is notable for his roles in "My Only 12%" (as Cake), "Between Us" (as Wiew), and "War of Y" (guest role).

In 2024, after participating in the South Korean survival show "Fantasy Boys," Santa joined GMMTV. He is currently pursuing a degree in Digital Marketing Communication and Branding at Rangsit University.
